de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.database.ids

Interface DoubleDBIDListIter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ArrayIter, DBIDArrayIter, DBIDIter, DBIDRef, Iter
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DoubleDBIDListMIter, DoubleIntegerDBIDListIter, DoubleIntegerDBIDListMIter
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DoubleIntegerDBIDList.Itr, DoubleIntegerDBIDPairKNNListHeap.Itr, DoubleIntegerDBIDPairList.Itr, IntegerDBIDKNNSubList.Itr, KNNSubList.Itr

    public interface DoubleDBIDListIter
extends DBIDArrayIter
    Iterator over double-DBID pairs results. There is no getter for the DBID, as this implements DBIDRef.
    Author:
    Erich Schubert

        DoubleDBIDPair getPair()
        Materialize an object pair. Note: currently, this will create a new object. In order to avoid the garbage collection overhead, it is preferable to use #doubleValue() and exploit that the iterator itself is a DBIDRef reference.
        Returns:
